It was revealed that the Queen is limiting the balcony appearance after the special Platinum Jubilee event to working royals only. Royal sources have now said the couple could make an appearance at the celebrations alongside other senior royals, possibly even as part of a second balcony appearance. A Palace source said: "Other family members will be invited to events. We've always made that clear and they are likely to be public events." PLEASE FOLLOW BELOW FOR LIVE UPDATES: